  <h1>Next Steps Guide - After Serving Your Notice</h1>

  <p><strong>Notice Type:</strong> {{#if (eq notice_route "section_21")}}Section 21 (No-Fault Eviction){{else}}Section 8 (Fault-Based Eviction){{/if}}</p>
