      <li>‚úì Proof you served prescribed information</li>
      <li>‚úì Copy of gas safety certificate</li>
      <li>‚úì Copy of EPC</li>
      <li>‚úì Proof you served "How to Rent" guide</li>
    {{/if}}
    <li>‚úì Any other evidence supporting your claim</li>
  </ul>

